public class AdminController
extends UserController
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable

Admin GUI Controller Class

Controls FMXL GUI elements for Admin class. Sub sections: 1. Leagues Tab Methods. 2. Teams Tab Methods. 3. Player/Venue Methods (Teams Tab). 4. Fixtures Tab Methods. 5. Score Sheet Methods (Fixtures Tab). 6. General Methods.
Since:
06/12/2020

    • generateFixtures

      public void generateFixtures​(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
      This generates a league style set of fixtures for the League selected in choiceBoxFixturesTabLeague. - Each team will play every other team in the league. - No team will play more than once a week. - Each team only plays another team once. - If there are an odd number of teams in the league, a 'bye' will be assigned once per week, where it is not possible for that team to play. - If "Generate home AND away fixtures" is selected, every team will play every other team in both a HOME and AWAY match (doubles the fixtures).
      Parameters:
      event - Generate Fixtures GUI button press.
